pve-microvm (0.1.5-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Restructure docs: concise README with demo GIF, detailed docs in docs/.
  * GUI: add 'microvm' to machine type dropdown, auto-set serial/vga.
  * Ship microvm-init for images without init (e.g., debian:trixie-slim).
  * Add virtio-balloon-device (mmio) — suppresses PVE balloon warning.
  * Fix OCI import init detection (systemd vs busybox vs minimal).
  * Default OCI image: debian:trixie-slim (28 MB).
  * Allow vga=serial0 for PVE web UI xterm.js console.
  * End-to-end tested: template → clone → boot → serial console.

 -- Rui Carmo <rui.carmo@gmail.com>  Fri, 18 Apr 2026 19:00:00 +0000

pve-microvm (0.1.4-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Set vga=serial0 so PVE web UI opens xterm.js serial console by default.
  * Tools auto-set --serial0 socket --vga serial0 and delete vmgenid/smbios1.
  * Default image changed to debian:trixie-slim (28 MB, same as PVE 9 host).
  * Support systemd images: enable serial-getty@ttyS0, set empty root password.
  * Fix bridge script path (/usr/libexec/qemu-server/).
  * Fix args quoting for -append with spaces.
  * Fix Perl module imports (Network.pm, Agent.pm).
  * Fix get_vm_machine +pve0 append for microvm.
  * Tested end-to-end on PVE 9.1.7 (z83ii).

 -- Rui Carmo <rui.carmo@gmail.com>  Fri, 18 Apr 2026 17:30:00 +0000

